Oven to 400

6 T butter 
6 T flour
2 c whole milk 

5 XL eggs
2 1/2 c grated swiss (gruyere) 

Optional additions:
chives
garlic
shallots
green onions
cooked potato
spanish chorizo
roasted red pepper

butter the dish
make the white sauce & cool
combine everything

bake 30-40 mins

  thanks jacques pepin!
